==English==

===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[transliteratus]]'' past participle of ''[[transliterare]]'' "to transliterate", from ''[[trans-]]'' "across" + ''[[littera]]'' "letter".

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The act or product of [[transliterating]], or of representing [[word]]s of a [[language]] by means of the [[character]]s of another [[alphabet]] or [[script]].

